A highly detailed, stylized illustration of a gleaming, ornate pistol – the Mystical Glock – radiating a faint blue aura, hovering slightly above a cracked, ancient cobblestone street in a bizarre, otherworldly cityscape reminiscent of a Vorthos plane. The pistol is intricately detailed with glowing runes and gears, a single bullet counter visibly hovering beside it. Rat-a-tat-tat style illustration, dark fantasy, magical, cinematic lighting.